					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13421705#post-4693715</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13421705/scp-4563#post-4693715</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2020 02:31:50 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Penguin6</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4857652</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Hey! The reason for the led lettering is simple: Plot. :p I read online that cockroaches are afraid of the color red, and so I took that to the extreme in that it’s a giant cockroach, it has giant red phobia. I’m also colorblind, so I understand that it’s not where colors are just black/white, but the intention was just as a fun gimmick to keep secrets secret.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13421705#post-4692903</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13421705/scp-4563#post-4692903</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2020 07:21:19 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Anarchie</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4535133</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>See, I have protanomaly - which isn't full protanopia at all, or what regular cockroaches, bees, and so on have. I can't say what red looks like to people without the ability to see it at all. To me, though, it shifts towards desaturated colors*, and from most things I've seen and heard, red usually shifts towards dark colors in almost all colorblindness types. So I'm not sure if 4563 has an anomalous sort of red colorblindness, because what's going on seems to be more like what'd occur if its vision was tinted red.</p> <p>*I have a dark mode with a brown background on and it made reading this article very confusing!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13421705#post-4692665</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13421705/scp-4563#post-4692665</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2020 00:52:15 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Dr Kensing</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5941791</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Well, as someone who knows several colorblind people, some colors just match other colors almost exactly. It’s probably the same thing for the cockroach, as red and white might look very similar to it.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
